snippet.title: Portal Knights - Coming Soon To Google Play Store
snippet.description: We’re excited to announce that Portal Knights, our award-winning cooperative sandbox action-RPG, is coming soon to the Google Play Store! It is available for pre-registration on the Google Play Store. Sign up here: http://bit.ly/2jw54zw
